==Usual Requirements==
In order to sortie to the event maps, players must fulfill the following requirements:

* Must have a 75% sortie win ratio
* Must have 5 empty ship slots for new ships
* Must have 20 free equipment slots
* Have a [[Combined Fleet]] for certain maps (see below)

Apart from the aforementioned hard-lined requirements, the players are recommended to prepare their fleet and resources for the upcoming events. See the [[Event#Tips|tips for preparations below]]
